 Desigual.=E2=80=9D (My guess is that=E2=80=99s a bit of an exaggeration, b=
ut that STL operates similarly to any of these other vulturous management f=
irms.) The lesson? Even when a brand is a business failure, there will be s=
omeone who believes that they can extract value from the goodwill it has ac=
